21-501.Short title.

Sections 21-501 to 21-542 shall be known and may be cited as the Nebraska Uniform Protected Series Act.

SourceLaws 2018, LB1121, ยง 2.

Cross ReferencesNebraska Uniform Limited Liability Company Act, see section 21-101.
